"40:5:15" : {s: 40, a: 5, w: 15, r: "دحض", t: "لِيُدْحِضُوا۟", l: "يُدْحِضُ", lc: 2, tl: "liyud'ḥiḍū", lb: "মিথ্যা প্রতিপন্ন করা, খণ্ডন করা",e: "to refute", b: "", i: "untuk melenyapkan", f: 2, rm: "slip, having no firmness/stability, become null & void, to anul/void/reject, examine into, to be weak, to jerk/decline, that which has no force/weight, to refute/condemn, to depart, to go away."},
