"40:7:23" : {s: 40, a: 7, w: 23, r: "تبع", t: "وَٱتَّبَعُوا۟", l: "ٱتَّبَعَ", lc: 136, tl: "wa-ittabaʿū", lb: "অনুসরণ করা",e: "and follow", b: "এবং তারা অনুসরণ করেছে", i: "dan mereka mengikuti", f: 10, rm: "follow/went or walked behind/after, overtook, pursue/investigate/examine/hunt, sought/reach/obtain it, prosecute/sue (for right/due or blood-revenge), succession of one to another, consecutive/successive, follower, imitator, continue the same course, aid/assist/help, come with, obey, desire/demand."},
